<div id="Copy">
  <h2>Check Your Flow</h2>
  <p>ActiveBudget is an open source budgeting application.  You can use it to track your cash flow and hours worked.  Categorize your expenses and manage your time across a number of jobs.</p>

  <h2>Developers Welcome</h2>
  <p>ActiveBudget is <%= link_to 'Ruby on Rails', 'http://rubyonrails.org' %>.  The project is managed at <%= link_to 'Google Code', 'http://code.google.com/p/activebudget/' %>. There is a fully <%= link_to 'RESTful API','http://code.google.com/p/activebudget/wiki/API' %>.  ActiveBudget is designed to be a learning tool for Rails developers.</p>
</div>

